                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14049823" author="knutanders" created="Wed, 2 Jul 2014 12:08:39 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;The attached patch, &lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12653569/12653569_d6644-1a.diff&quot; title=&quot;d6644-1a.diff attached to DERBY-6644&quot;&gt;d6644-1a.diff&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, changes the parser so that &lt;tt&gt;ALTER TABLE t ALTER COLUMN c SET NOT NULL&lt;/tt&gt; is an alias for &lt;tt&gt;ALTER TABLE t ALTER COLUMN c NOT NULL&lt;/tt&gt;, and &lt;tt&gt;ALTER TABLE t ALTER COLUMN c DROP NOT NULL&lt;/tt&gt; is an alias for &lt;tt&gt;ALTER TABLE t ALTER COLUMN c NULL&lt;/tt&gt;. The patch also changes the existing test cases for &lt;tt&gt;ALTER COLUMN c [NOT] NULL&lt;/tt&gt; in AlterTableTest so that they test both the old syntax and the standard syntax.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;All regression tests passed with the patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14050323" author="dagw" created="Wed, 2 Jul 2014 17:58:26 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 to this change. Thanks for this, Knut!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14051153" author="jira-bot" created="Thu, 3 Jul 2014 08:49:22 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1607559 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=knutanders&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;knutanders&quot;&gt;Knut Anders Hatlen&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;code/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1607559&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1607559&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-6644&quot; title=&quot;Support standard syntax for altering column nullability&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DERBY-6644&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;DERBY-6644&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Support standard syntax for altering column nullability&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Implement SQL:2011 syntax for altering nullability:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  ALTER TABLE t ALTER COLUMN c SET NOT NULL&lt;br/&gt;
  ALTER TABLE t ALTER COLUMN c DROP NOT NULL&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14051154" author="knutanders" created="Thu, 3 Jul 2014 08:50:06 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, Dag. I&apos;ve committed the patch to trunk. Resolving the issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
